54
00:02:17,228 --> 00:02:19,680
Look, I didn't kill Cyrus, Keith.

55
00:02:19,681 --> 00:02:21,553
Niether did Hank Landry.

56
00:02:21,754 --> 00:02:23,414
But someone did.

57
00:02:24,164 --> 00:02:27,361
Well, let me dig around.
If I find anything, I'll take the case.

58
00:02:27,362 --> 00:02:28,841
Thank you.

59
00:02:38,808 --> 00:02:41,398
Wow, this is one trashed lab.

60
00:02:41,399 --> 00:02:44,216
All that's missing is a big hole
in the wall shaped like the Hulk

61
00:02:46,037 --> 00:02:47,932
